# Example names for configuring OpenAI-compatible gateways when using
# OpenAICompatRouterClassifier in your own application (never commit .env).
# Base URL must be the API root including /v1 (do not append /chat/completions).
#
# OpenRouter:
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...
# OPENROUTER_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
#
# Generic OpenAI-compatible:
API_KEY=
BASE_URL=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=
